snippet.title: Genso Manège | Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Follow Emma as she fights to reawaken her magical powers in order to aid a unique cast of characters, all of whom are trapped inside a travelling amusement park. Having lost memories from youth, Emma must rediscover her past through love and friendship in this stunning dream-like fantasy otome.

Wishlist Now - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2497670/Genso_Mange/
